<a name="l00042"></a><a class="code" href="class_sample.html">00042</a> <span class="keyword">class </span><a class="code" href="class_sample.html" title="Sample is like Oscil, it plays a wavetable, but defaults to playing once through, from start to finis...">Sample</a>
